N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 213.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

The purpose of this Part is to establish a process by which
entities may be recognized and approved by the Commission as promoters of
professional wrestling to oversee and conduct professional wrestling events in
the State of New York. Notes
